        </div>
        <img class="description-card__img" src="/assets/images/Home/Nuffield-1.jpg" alt="" role="presentation"/>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12">
      <div class="description-card">
        <img class="description-card__img" src="/assets/images/Home/Dot-vote-sketch.jpg" alt="" role="presentation"/>
        <div class="description-card__text">
          <h2 class="h3">Using digital to bring ingenuity to life</h2>
          <p>From strategic thinking to detailed service and product design – to complex engineering and bleeding edge experimentation, we’re proud to drive innovation and enrich people’s lives. We create a positive human future in a technology driven world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">  
    <div class="col col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12 offset-lg-2">
      <div class="description-card description-card--reverse">
        <div class="description-card__text">
          <h2 class="h3">The best team you’ll ever work with, in the best job you’ll ever have</h2>
          <p>Our teams are trusted to deliver and given the space to be awesome. We’re an inclusive community for the curious, generous, pragmatic and enthusiastic digital practitioner.</p>
        </div>
        <img class="description-card__img" src="/assets/images/Home/Design-team1.jpg" alt="" role="presentation"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col offset-lg-8 col-lg-4 col-12 decoration decoration--long-rectangle"></div> 
</div>

